dcterms:description: A dataset created from the Internet2 topology and dynamic SFC requests, containing a total of 14735 lists for active requests, with each list averaging 26.08 requests. The dataset was generated using an ILP-based placement algorithm to determine the optimal number and location of VNF instances.
dcterms:title: Internet2 Topology and Dynamic SFC Requests
